      "name": "Misty Escape",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/aura.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>If the vampire drops to 0 Pontos de Vida outside its resting place, the vampire uses Mudar de Forma to become mist (no action required). If it can't use Mudar de Forma, it is destroyed.\nWhile it has 0 Pontos de Vida in mist form, it can't return to its vampire form, and it must alcance its resting place within 2 hours or be destroyed. Once in its resting place, it returns to its vampire form and fica com a condição Paralisado until it regains any Pontos de Vida, and it regains 1 Hit Point after spending 1 hour there.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
