        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The vampire casts Charm Person, requiring no spell components and using Carisma as the spellcasting ability (spell save CD 17), and the duration is 24 hours. The Enfeitiçado target is a willing recipient of the vampire's Mordida, the de dano of which doesn't end the spell. When the spell ends, o alvo is unaware it was Enfeitiçado by the vampire.</p>",
